name: Atarisoft Collection
overview: The 1984 Atarisoft collection for the Commodore 64 was created by Bandit Breaking Service and includes all the AtariSoft games for the C64 with the exception of Battlezone and Galaxian. Games included: ◉ Centipede ◉ Defender ◉ Dig Dug ◉ Donkey Kong ◉ Jungle Hunt ◉ Moon Patrol ◉ Ms. Pacman ◉ Pac-Man ◉ Pole Position ◉ Robotron: 2084
